Full Description: webScurity is all about web application security. webScurity Inc. was founded in 2001 to serve the needs of a large financial institution, who, despite state-of-the-art perimeter defenses (firewalls, IDS/IPS, etc.) suffered a serious security breach. Comprehensive application assessment policies were quickly instituted to make sure all Web applications adhered to secure coding guidelines before becoming available to customers, partners, and/or vendors over the Internet. Description: Healthcare Software Tool
Full Description: OpCoder AI is a healthcare software tool that processes surgical operative notes using artificial intelligence and natural language processing to accurately assign CPT billing codes. By working as both a supplement to human coders and an auditing tool for hospital administrators, OpCoder AI revolutionizes the efficiency and accuracy of the hospital reimbursement process. As a tool to supplement human coders, OpCoder AI dramatically increases processing capacity and efficiency, allowing daily targets and coder output to be increased 10x. As a tool for administrative personnel, OpCoder AI allows for high-level auditing and assessment of the billing process and for early identification of problem operative notes. By doing so, OpCoder AI eliminates miscoding, saving coders time and saving hospitals money.
Industry Groups: Artificial Intelligence (AI), Data and Analytics, Health Care, Science and Engineering, Software
